❗️The temple has 1008 idols of Lord Shiva which includes 12 Jyotirlingas. The temple 135 feet long supported by 1200 pillars ad has 108 rooms and t and the tomb of Guru Madhavanand Ji is built in the centre of the premises. 

❗️This Om Shaped temple is known as Om Shiv Mandir and this temple is situated in Jaddan village, Pali district, Rajasthan. It is built in 270 acres and the foundation of this temple was laid in the year 1995 and now it is in a final stages of construction.
